# Project Overview

The Student Management Information System is a full-stack web application developed to manage student information efficiently. The system allows students to register, login, store educational details, and view their information through a personalized dashboard.

The project is designed using modern web technologies and demonstrates frontend development, backend development, database integration, authentication, API communication, and responsive design.

