```

---

# API Endpoints

## Register Student

```http
POST /submit
```

Stores student information in MongoDB.

---

## Login Student

```http
POST /login
```

Authenticates student credentials.

---

## Get Student Details

```http
GET /api/student/:id
```

Returns student information.

---

## Update Education Details

```http
POST /api/education/:id
```

Updates academic records.

